# Exam Result Email Automation — Context Brief

> Optimized for Claude Code sessions. Read this first when resuming work.

## What This Is

A Windows desktop app (PySide6) for university Registrar Office staff to generate and send personalized exam result emails from an Excel spreadsheet via Microsoft Outlook or SMTP.

## Current State

- **Version:** 0.7.0
- **Tests:** 143 passing (`source .venv/bin/activate && python3 -m pytest -q`)
- **Platform:** Windows target, macOS development (Python 3.12 venv)
- **Branch:** main — Sprint 7 complete

## Quick Commands

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate       # Python 3.12 venv (REQUIRED — system Python 3.9 won't work)
python3 -m pytest -q            # 120 tests in ~0.9s
python3 app.py                  # Launch GUI
```

